<li role="presentation"><a href='?term="Appl%20Ergon"[jour]' class="usa-link" role="menuitem" data-add-to-search="true">Add to search</a></li>
</ul></nav></section><section class="front-matter"><div class="ameta p font-secondary font-xs">
<hgroup><h1>Subtle cues: Qualitative elicitation of signs of capacity strain in the hospital workplace</h1></hgroup><div class="cg p">
<a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Womack%20DM"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id1"><span class="name western">Dana M Womack</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id1">
<h3><span class="name western">Dana M Womack</span></h3>
<div class="p">
<sup>a)</sup>Oregon Health &amp; Science University, Department of Medical Informatics &amp; Clinical Epidemiology, 3181 S.W. Sam Jackson Park Rd., Portland, Oregon 97239-3098</div>
<div class="p">Find articles by <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Womack%20DM"[Author]' class="usa-link"><span class="name western">Dana M Womack</span></a>
</div>
