<col align="left" valign="middle" span="1">
<col align="left" valign="middle" span="1">
</colgroup>
<thead><tr>
<th align="left" valign="top" rowspan="1" colspan="1">Level of Capacity Strain</th>
<th align="left" valign="top" rowspan="1" colspan="1">Proposed definition</th>
</tr></thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td align="left" valign="top" rowspan="1" colspan="1">Calamity</td>
<td align="left" valign="top" rowspan="1" colspan="1">Altered mode of functioning in response to a disaster-level event (out of scope for this study)</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="left" valign="top" rowspan="1" colspan="1">Really Stretched</td>
